Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.62,0:05:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是金太郎糖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.89,0:05:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论怎么切 都是金太郎糖哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很少见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有好多小忍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.48,0:05:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日本的物品都和小忍很像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,金太郎…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.01,0:05:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍微修改一下长度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.99,0:05:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.08,0:05:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 已经可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.75,0:05:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.37,0:05:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们负责制作菜单
