Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.98,0:05:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord0\c&H000000&\fr-25\fs18\pos(249.1,328.666)}茶杯咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.98,0:05:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord0\c&H000000&\fr-25\fs18\pos(287.525,382)}绿茶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.58,0:05:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因为是我们想出来的菜单啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.67,0:05:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近的超市是哪里来着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.15,0:05:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是北口的超市吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.49,0:06:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔 小绫 出发啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.14,0:06:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.49,0:06:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小绫去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.05,0:06:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 去买材料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.89,0:06:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 茶叶就拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.03,0:06:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.43,0:06:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,碎巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.96,0:06:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蜜豆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.95,0:06:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糯米粉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.62,0:06:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天想吃汉堡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.13,0:06:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天吃什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.94,0:06:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 汉堡之类的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.91,0:06:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和你只是普通朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.85,0:06:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么突然这么说！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.78,0:06:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶 乌丸酱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.78,0:06:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 被你们发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.64,0:06:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来买学园祭用的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.52,0:06:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.69,0:06:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乌丸老师呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.22,0:06:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来买一点零食
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.92,0:06:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个时间吃会变胖的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 因为是豆腐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.12,0:06:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,豆腐是零食？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.05,0:06:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特意连酱油都买了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.71,0:07:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.97,0:07:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.22,0:07:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小路同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.25,0:07:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想确认一下服装的号码
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.75,0:07:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是穿和服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.93,0:07:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶 因为
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.36,0:07:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,猪熊同学和大宫同学说…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.79,0:07:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么想 绫都应该穿这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.39,0:07:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得很适合你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 别随随便便就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.54,0:07:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然准备工作很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.31,0:07:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是还真叫人期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.64,0:07:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.51,0:08:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说来小忍 你还记得明天是什么日子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.42,0:08:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是学园祭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.98,0:08:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 说的不是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.23,0:08:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.14,0:08:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想想 也不是什么节日呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.52,0:08:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不是谁的生日呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.38,0:08:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,纪念日？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.70,0:08:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关于什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.21,0:08:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不记得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我记得的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.84,0:08:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对于艾莉丝来说是很重要的日子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.08,0:08:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个 是什么日子来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.85,0:08:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.01,0:08:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那个 艾莉丝第一次开口说话的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.61,0:08:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一次去海边的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.19,0:08:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.33,0:08:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉丝 艾莉丝在暗示什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.61,0:08:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.44,0:08:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.64,0:09:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我想不起来的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.59,0:09:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉丝变得无精打采了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.64,0:09:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 得赶紧想起来才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.77,0:09:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在睡着之前竭尽全力地想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.53,0:09:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个 小忍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.78,0:09:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天是…
