Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:15:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\an8}谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:16:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多到换班的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.25,0:16:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.21,0:16:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来参观一下学园祭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.15,0:16:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 金色的头发
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.92,0:16:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 很美味
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.68,0:16:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢惠顾
