Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 艾莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,学园祭玩得开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.59,0:17:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很美味
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.81,0:17:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.72,0:17:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们从刚才起就光顾着吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可怜的戏剧马上就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.49,0:17:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,演出的节目是白雪公主
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.84,0:17:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是老剧情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.94,0:17:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可怜扮演什么角色呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.93,0:17:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢白雪公主了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.49,0:18:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和恋爱有关的她都喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.83,0:18:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开演了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白雪公主
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.71,0:18:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.36,0:18:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.55,0:18:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来祛除她身上的妖魔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.03,0:18:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,处斩了区区妖魔…是也
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.03,0:18:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.01,0:18:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢光临
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.14,0:18:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得有点寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.66,0:18:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.61,0:19:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.05,0:19:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个 一定要交给她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.93,0:19:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忍…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.56,0:19:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忍…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.00,0:19:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忍…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.52,0:19:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得从刚才开始一直有人在叫“死”啊“死”啊的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.52,0:19:26.18,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs21\an7}注：日文中“死”与“忍”的第一个假名均为“し（shi）”
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.18,0:19:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么 好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.37,0:19:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,磨磨蹭蹭的 学园祭都已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.86,0:19:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.74,0:19:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起去扔垃圾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.24,0:19:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,机会来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.78,0:19:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶 艾莉丝手上拿的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.16,0:19:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是垃圾吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.88,0:19:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就一起扔掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.78,0:19:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我又说错什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.83,0:19:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小忍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.70,0:20:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.96,0:20:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.82,0:20:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请…请你收下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.75,0:20:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,礼物？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.62,0:20:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.78,0:20:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.88,0:20:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小忍以前不是送了这只簪子给我当礼物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.85,0:20:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想回礼给你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.10,0:20:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你能喜欢就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天使…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.56,0:20:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,金发的天使…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.17,0:20:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小忍 振作起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.78,0:20:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可爱的缎带
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.42,0:20:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉丝每天都戴着簪子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.77,0:20:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我也戴上 当做亮点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.43,0:20:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.64,0:20:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:20:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特别适合你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.79,0:21:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.35,0:21:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.11,0:21:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.17,0:21:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小忍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.38,0:21:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的头怎么搞的 等人来吐槽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.12,0:21:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 月代头
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.08,0:21:19.29,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs21\an7}注：明治维新以前日本男子常梳的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.73,0:21:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这枚缎带…还是用来观赏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.02,0:21:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 明明这么可爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,——ed——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.11,0:23:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近有一个很喜欢的日语短语
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.02,0:23:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.06,0:23:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.24,0:23:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算变得消沉 也能重新振作
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.03,0:23:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魔法般的词语哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.20,0:23:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.26,0:23:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\pos(424,62)}别担心的由来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.32,0:23:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日语！好棒啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.35,0:23:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小忍有什么纪念日吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.38,0:23:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自从艾莉丝到来 每天都是纪念日！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.82,0:23:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\shad0\fs25\pos(298.125,63.333)\fad(0,200)}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.21,0:23:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小忍…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.93,0:23:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过 如果一定要说的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.27,0:23:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上周吃过的新款杯面很好吃 就把那天当做杯面纪念日…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.82,0:23:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爽滑有嚼劲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.45,0:23:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&H000000&\fs25\3c&H000000&\shad0\fr15\pos(290.175,68.668)}是谁还没睡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.06,0:23:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night
